VITALI ATOM'S EFFECT ON EACH LEVEL
============================================================
Does Vitali atom preserve sigma?
  Sigma preserved: 0
  Sigma changed: 123
  Max |delta_sigma|: 1
  This means Vitali atoms live BETWEEN Level 1 and Level 1.5!
